data.description: REDUCED...4-bedroom home offers a comfortable, 1,499 sqft of living space as well as a screened patio/lanai & a fenced back yard. Home features a modern, open, great room floor plan and is perfect for family gatherings or entertaining. The open kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining and great room area. A convenient breakfast bar encourages conversation and culinary creativity. Step outside onto the screened lanai, a tranquil space to enjoy the Florida weather and sunshine at your leisure. The fenced backyard offers privacy and is the ideal setting for children to play or for pets to roam freely. The two-car garage provides ample additional storage and parking protection from the elements. Equipped with stainless steel appliances, the kitchen is both functional and stylish, making meal preparation a breeze. With its thoughtful design, this home combines comfort, convenience and a touch of outdoor serenity, making it the perfect place to raise a young family or to retire and call home. An added perk...there is access to xFinity internet / cable service to the address! Call now to schedule your private viewing of the home. Thank you for considering my listing...
